OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778875555
OL,3,CValdo Calocane's brother thought
OL,4,Cviolent messages were about suicide
OL,6,FAsked by Ms Langdale what he thought
OL,7,Fof this message, Elias Calocane said:
OL,8,F"I'm not sure at the time what I
OL,9,Fthought exactly.
OL,11,F"The whole conversation is about
OL,12,Fpraying or asking something to take
OL,13,Fthat away and coming into a new sense
OL,14,Fof peace that you can't quite explain.
OL,16,F"I thought he was saying something of
OL,17,Fthe same sort of vein.
OL,19,F"I definitely didn't associate it with
OL,20,Fmurder."
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778875555
OL,3,CValdo Calocane's brother thought
OL,4,Cviolent messages were about suicide
OL,6,FElias Calocane said his brother used a
OL,7,F"religious context of asking God or
OL,8,Fpraying" for his pain to be taken away.
OL,10,FCalocane told his brother he had an
OL,11,Fencounter with the holy spirit and was
OL,12,F"saved", the inquiry heard.
OL,14,FCalocane also told his brother:
OL,15,F"Either something extraordinary is
OL,16,Fhappening or I'm losing my mind."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@HO]tD@AOUtD@GO]wD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778875555
OL,3,CValdo Calocane's brother thought
OL,4,Cviolent messages were about suicide
OL,6,FAsked if he was worried his brother
OL,7,Fwas losing his mind, Elias Calocane
OL,8,Fsaid: "I'm not sure how I took that
OL,9,Fmessage on its own, except the fact I
OL,10,Fwanted him to explain more.
OL,12,F"Obviously I'm worried, I'm trying to
OL,13,Ffigure out what's happening."
OL,15,FThe inquiry heard that Calocane
OL,16,F"flipped out" when his mother Celeste
OL,17,Fcalled him without warning in March
OL,18,F2020, before telling her never to do
OL,19,Fit again.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUuD@]O]xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778875555
OL,3,CValdo Calocane's brother thought
OL,4,Cviolent messages were about suicide
OL,6,FAsked if Calocane was argumentative
OL,7,Fgrowing up, his brother said he would
OL,8,F"prefer to sort of like withdraw a
OL,9,Flittle bit", which he added was
OL,10,F"significant in hindsight".
OL,12,FThe inquiry heard that Elias Calocane
OL,13,Ftried to convince his brother that
OL,14,Ftechnology could not see the things he
OL,15,Fwas looking at.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@KO]rD@AOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
