OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778875555
OL,3,CValdo Calocane's brother thought
OL,4,Cviolent messages were about suicide
OL,6,FThe witness said: "I was trying to
OL,7,Fsort of come at it with what I felt
OL,8,Fwas a logical perspective of trying to
OL,9,Fconvince him that these things were
OL,10,Funlikely to even exist or if they
OL,11,Fexisted, that it would be quite
OL,12,Fadvanced technology that would be
OL,13,Freserved for sort of national security
OL,14,Fagencies and stuff like that.
OL,16,F"So you begin rationally trying to
OL,17,Ftell him that can't be the case."
OL,19,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@nD@SOUxD@AOUyD@aO]
